Adapter  design  pattern  is  A  structural design pattern

Adapter  design  Pattern  ensures  that  tht  app code base  reamins maintainable
while using  the  3rd  party codebase

It  allows  the  interface  of  an  existing  class  to be
used  as  another  interface.

often  used  to make  existing class  work with  others without
modifying  their  source  code.
s

Helps in loosely coupling  our  apps code base




